Package: bleux-features
Section: utils
Depends: apt
Recommends: gnome-software,
    volian-archive-keyring,
    volian-archive-nala
Suggests: flatpak,
    gnome-software-plugin-flatpak,
    gnome-software-plugin-snap,
    libspa-0.2-bluetooth,
    libspa-0.2-jack,
    nala,
    pipewire-audio-client-libraries,
    pulseaudio,
    pulseaudio-module-bluetooth,
    snapd,
    wireplumber | pipewire-media-session
Description: The bleUX feature scripts
 This package has scripts to toggle the core features of the bleUX desktop
 system.
Files: fix-python3-typer.list /usr/lib/bleux-features/
    fix-python3-typer.pref /usr/lib/bleux-features/
    nosnap.pref /usr/lib/bleux-features/
    scripts/apt-disable /usr/bin/
    scripts/apt-disabled /usr/bin/
    scripts/apt-enable /usr/bin/
    scripts/flatpak-add /usr/bin/
    scripts/flatpak-remove /usr/bin/
